name: Kishu Baby
description: The Lovely KISHUBABY was created on 27th June 2021 with the goal of being a decentralized meme project with a true purpose. The Cute small BabyDoge brother, Kishu Baby want to grow up with an awesome team with highly skilled devs, first class marketing people, and constantly ever-growing community. In the first 3 hours after launched in BSC network, KISHUBABY made an historic hype to $5 milion market cap with more than 3,300 holders. That is community driven token, where they are involved on token decisions, like choose an anti whale system, voting to burn tokens each week, do airdrops, or even donate some to charity projects, all carried out in the official telegram groups: https://t.me/KishuBaby for english and https://t.me/KishuBabyEsp for spanish language. The contract is verified in the BSC and the liquidity locked that makes the investors safe with it. It is also integrated a smart staking system built in to reward the holders with 5% of each transaction, so more KISHUBABY tokens are being automatically added to the wallet of each holder. Simply Lovely KISHUBABY, Cute BABYDOGE's small brother, stay tuned to see how it grows.
